        <div class=3D"hero-inner">
          <div>
            <div class=3D"eyebrow">A memoir about image, authority, record,=
 and the private systems that decide what counts as truth</div>
            <h1><span class=3D"title-italic">Paper Walls</span><br>The Arch=
itecture of Control</h1>
            <p class=3D"hero-copy">
              Raised in a carefully curated Los Angeles household where app=
earance governed belonging, Hsin-Neh Rogers traces how narrative becomes au=
thority=E2=80=94and what it costs to challenge a version of reality already=
 assigned.
            </p>
            <div class=3D"hero-actions">
              <a class=3D"button primary" href=3D"file:///Users/hsin-neh/Do=
